			(property "Description" "Core  Arm 32-bit Cortex-M0+ CPU with memory protection unit, frequency up to 80 MHz  Operating characteristics  Extended temperature: 40C up to 125C  Wide supply voltage range: 1.62 V to 3.6 V  Memories  Up to 128KB of flash memory with error correction code (ECC)  Up to 32KB of SRAM with hardware parity  High-performance analog peripherals  Two simultaneous sampling 12-bit 4-Msps analog-to-digital converters (ADCs) with up to 17 external channels  14-bit effective resolution"
